FBIS3-1206 "drafr056_e_94002" FBIS-AFR-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 WEST AFRICA Burkina Faso New Prime Minister's Background Outlined AB2203171794 Ouagadougou Radiodiffusion Nationale du Burkina Radio in French 0630 GMT 22 Mar 94 AB2203171794 Ouagadougou Radiodiffusion Nationale du Burkina Radio Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] New Prime Minister Roch Marc Christian Kabore yesterday granted an exclusive interview to Radio Burkina. The current prime minister, appointed by presidential decree, is not new to the political scene. He is 37 years old and has held successive posts as minister of transport and communications from 1989 to 1990, minister of state from 1990 to 1992, minister of state in charge of finance and planning from 1992 to 1993, and then minister in charge of relations with institutions.
